title: UlisesSoft NodLogin 10.0.4
description:
New NodLogin 10.0.4

All previous versions will stop working.

The NodLogin is compatible with all products and all
ESET versions (2.7, 3.0, 4.0, 4.2)

As you know NodLogin not a crack, not a patch, not a fix.
The NodLogin not modify any files or windows antivirus,
does not change the antivirus logs and under windows, so
All it does is put a valid license antivirus, take
that profits are recognized as false positives, and
ESET puts its virus signature database, so that the antivirus
delete it from your PC.

To remove the antivirus utility, you should exclude
folder where you unzip the NodLogin while excluding
also the folder where you installed the NodLogin.
C: \ Program Files \ UlisesSoft \
If you exclude the folder will not have problems with false positive
and remove antivirus utility.

For the Anti-Virus 4.x
----------------------------------
ESET recently blocked nodlogin web server and running the
nodlogin gives a message that I could not connect to database
This is solved in this way:
1. Login to antivirus
2. Press F5
3. Enter the menu:
Antivirus and Antispyware>> Protection of Internet traffic>> Management
Address
In this window we select:
List of excluded addresses filtering:
Press the Add button and enter:
* Ulisessoft * (astericoulisessoftasterisco)
This will exclude the (ww.ulisessoft.info) List
Antivirus filtering and thus will not block when connecting to NodLogin
to the database (it sends an image of the configuration).

Important:
-----------------
If running NodLogin gives the message "No match
valid licenses now "is because the database
NodLogin not have valid licenses, this happens generally for
the products ESET Smart Security "and that the licenses for the
product are low, just be patient until they update
database.

PS: Note that there are 2 files one for 32bit and one 64bit.

Attached files: nl10.0.4_32bits.rar and nl10.0.4_64bits.rar
